==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skippet
<hw>Skip"pet</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Icel.
<ets>skip</ets>, E. <ets>skipper</ets>. See <er>Ship</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A small boat; a skiff.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A little <qex>skippet</qex> floating did appear.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A small round box for keeping records.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skippingly</ent>⟦br⟧
